1
00:01:20,480 --> 00:01:21,920
That thing should be gone, right?

2
00:01:46,640 --> 00:01:49,320
Why is this room sealed shut?

3
00:01:58,600 --> 00:02:00,200
This joss paper was just burned.

4
00:02:01,040 --> 00:02:02,480
And the room is sealed shut.

5
00:02:03,120 --> 00:02:06,960
Looks like someone was secretly mourning the dead here.

6
00:02:10,480 --> 00:02:11,960
Why are these claw marks so strange?

7
00:02:12,840 --> 00:02:13,960
Could they be from that monster?

8
00:02:15,320 --> 00:02:17,280
I saw claw marks like these in the corridor too.

9
00:02:18,000 --> 00:02:21,360
And dried bloodstains and ghostly words written in blood.

10
00:02:33,000 --> 00:02:34,640
A stunning glance

11
00:02:35,200 --> 00:02:36,560
Unequaled in the world

12
00:02:38,880 --> 00:02:40,640
This used to be Shuang'er's room.

13
00:02:41,600 --> 00:02:45,600
So they were mourning Shuang'er just now.

14
00:03:00,200 --> 00:03:01,000
Master

15
00:03:03,760 --> 00:03:07,160
Master, that vengeful spirit in the tree kept chasing me.

16
00:03:07,920 --> 00:03:10,400
Luckily, Mr. Zheng showed up and saved me.

17
00:03:11,240 --> 00:03:14,840
I thought I'd never see you again in this life, Master.

18
00:03:14,840 --> 00:03:17,200
Don't be scared, don't be scared.

19
00:03:17,640 --> 00:03:19,360
Master Wang, you should help me as soon as possible.

20
00:03:19,400 --> 00:03:20,960
And disperse Shuang'er's vengeful spirit.

21
00:03:21,200 --> 00:03:23,280
Or the Wang family's troubles will only grow.

22
00:03:26,960 --> 00:03:27,800
Fifth Concubine

23
00:03:28,480 --> 00:03:30,760
You should go back and rest first.

24
00:03:31,320 --> 00:03:32,560
All right, Master.

25
00:03:32,800 --> 00:03:33,800
It's good that you're all right.

26
00:03:41,160 --> 00:03:41,760
Have a seat.

27
00:03:47,360 --> 00:03:51,960
Was it really Shuang'er's spirit chasing you just now?

28
00:03:54,520 --> 00:03:55,480
It should be.

29
00:03:56,040 --> 00:03:58,360
It was too dark just now to see clearly.

30
00:04:03,760 --> 00:04:04,440
By the way,

31
00:04:04,680 --> 00:04:09,120
I just saw those two paper figurines talking.

32
00:04:11,160 --> 00:04:12,840
No wonder the paper figurines vanished.

33
00:04:13,720 --> 00:04:15,800
Once a paper figurine has absorbed enough malice,

34
00:04:16,040 --> 00:04:18,280
it will seek revenge on those who harmed it.

35
00:04:19,720 --> 00:04:21,000
Could it be that Master Wang

36
00:04:21,320 --> 00:04:23,560
did something to wrong them before?

37
00:04:23,640 --> 00:04:24,440
Well...

38
00:04:26,680 --> 00:04:29,440
Shuang'er's vengeful spirit has set its sights on you now.

39
00:04:29,440 --> 00:04:31,520
If you still keep silent,

40
00:04:31,600 --> 00:04:35,920
I'm afraid your life will be in danger, Master Wang.

41
00:04:43,720 --> 00:04:48,680
Back then, my Sanming insisted on marrying that prostitute.

42
00:04:49,040 --> 00:04:51,280
After all, he was my own son.

43
00:04:51,440 --> 00:04:54,240
I couldn't outstubborn him, so I agreed.

44
00:04:54,680 --> 00:04:58,480
Who knew that Shuang'er was so promiscuous?

45
00:04:58,920 --> 00:05:02,360
She was secretly committing adultery with a servant behind our backs.

46
00:05:04,360 --> 00:05:06,440
My Sanming was too enraged to bear it.

47
00:05:06,560 --> 00:05:07,960
In a fit of rage, he lost control

48
00:05:08,240 --> 00:05:10,440
and killed Shuang'er and that adulterer.

49
00:05:10,960 --> 00:05:14,200
My wife feared it would ruin Sanming's career.

50
00:05:14,560 --> 00:05:16,000
So she lied to the public,

51
00:05:16,960 --> 00:05:18,920
saying Shuang'er died of illness.

52
00:05:19,480 --> 00:05:20,920
From then on,

53
00:05:21,000 --> 00:05:23,360
strange things kept happening in the Wang family.

54
00:05:23,440 --> 00:05:27,920
That is why we asked you and your master to do Bone-gathering.

55
00:05:30,560 --> 00:05:33,880
So that is why you forced my master

56
00:05:33,880 --> 00:05:35,800
to gather bones with a living person's right hand.

57
00:05:39,320 --> 00:05:40,160
And then?

58
00:05:40,960 --> 00:05:43,880
What happened to your Wang family after that?

59
00:05:44,800 --> 00:05:47,160
We thought the Bone-gathering had succeeded.

60
00:05:47,160 --> 00:05:49,280
But who knew that that very night,

61
00:05:49,280 --> 00:05:52,320
Sanming suddenly went mad as if possessed.

62
00:05:58,920 --> 00:06:00,680
Yes, yes, yes, hurry up.

63
00:06:00,680 --> 00:06:01,560
Hurry up.

64
00:06:24,640 --> 00:06:26,560
No!

65
00:06:26,800 --> 00:06:32,080
My son!

66
00:06:34,760 --> 00:06:36,200
It has been three years.

67
00:06:37,000 --> 00:06:41,080
That woman's malice still has not faded.

68
00:06:41,480 --> 00:06:43,240
As long as her enemy is still alive,

69
00:06:43,720 --> 00:06:45,360
the malice will not disperse.

70
00:06:49,160 --> 00:06:50,160
Mr. Zheng

71
00:06:51,000 --> 00:06:53,840
We paid a great sum to bring you here.

72
00:06:54,600 --> 00:06:55,640
No matter what,

73
00:06:55,640 --> 00:06:58,240
you must help the Wang family end this disaster.

74
00:06:58,920 --> 00:07:01,120
Otherwise, don't blame me.

75
00:07:01,320 --> 00:07:02,760
Master Wang, there's no need to worry.

76
00:07:03,120 --> 00:07:04,200
I have my own way.

77
00:07:04,320 --> 00:07:06,760
The Bone-gathering ritual will proceed as usual.

78
00:07:12,120 --> 00:07:13,320
Come out.

79
00:07:17,680 --> 00:07:18,480
How did it go?

80
00:07:19,280 --> 00:07:21,280
Don't worry, no one noticed.

81
00:07:21,520 --> 00:07:22,320
I didn't expect

82
00:07:22,320 --> 00:07:24,800
that you used paper figurines to force him to tell the past.

83
00:07:25,160 --> 00:07:27,240
What that old fox Wang Shengchang said

84
00:07:27,560 --> 00:07:28,880
can only be half believed.

85
00:07:31,760 --> 00:07:33,400
That thing that attacked me,

86
00:07:33,640 --> 00:07:34,960
was it human or a ghost?

87
00:07:36,640 --> 00:07:37,960
Whether it is human or ghost,

88
00:07:38,480 --> 00:07:40,880
if it harmed people, we'll find a way to deal with it.

89
00:07:42,520 --> 00:07:46,040
I'm afraid he harmed those previous concubines too.

90
00:07:48,520 --> 00:07:50,440
You married into the Wang family

91
00:07:51,280 --> 00:07:53,080
to investigate your sister's death, didn't you?

92
00:07:58,320 --> 00:08:01,320
Risking yourself may not bring revenge.

93
00:08:02,120 --> 00:08:03,400
Instead, it may cost you your life.

94
00:08:03,400 --> 00:08:04,200
Do you know that?

95
00:08:04,320 --> 00:08:07,600
You knew how dangerous the Wang family was, yet you came too.

96
00:08:09,280 --> 00:08:11,120
You and I have both done this for the one most important to us.

97
00:08:11,880 --> 00:08:14,080
We have long cast life and death aside.
